<node CREATED="1282835459109" FOLDED="true" ID="Freemind_Link_820473261" MODIFIED="1282835461265" TEXT="CPM">
<node CREATED="1282836560250" ID="Freemind_Link_375465053" MODIFIED="1282836586687" TEXT="1. CPM: Calculate early start &amp; finish (Forward pass) and late start &amp; finish date (backward pass) of all activities without regard for any resource limitation by performing forward and backward pass on schedule network&#xa;2. Positive difference between early and late date termed as total float&#xa;3. Critical path have either zero or negative total float&#xa;4. Schedule activities on CP called critical activities&#xa;5. Free float, the amount of time that an activity can be delayed without delaying the early start date of any immediate successor activity within the network path"/>
</node>
